      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "waku uses BOTH: Claude Code writes waku's code - pi is waku's delegate_task sub-agent,\non whatever model the loop is running. pi refused to build sub-agents \u2014 which is exactly what makes it embeddable as one.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "rec-0040",
      "originalText": "waku uses BOTH: Claude Code writes waku's code - pi is waku's delegate_task sub-agent,\non whatever model the loop is running. pi refused to build sub-agents \u2014 which is exactly what makes it embeddable as one.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
